  "body": "### Overview\r\nMost of Brownie's features that use the GUI could probably be replicated just as easily in a TUI or CUI library. For example, coverage is just text display with colored highlights. #151 might be easier to implement this way too.\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\nSome library suggestions:\r\n- https://github.com/jwlodek/py_cui (really nice looking)\r\n- https://github.com/urwid/urwid (old)\r\n- https://github.com/peterbrittain/asciimatics (used by [Shadowlands](https://github.com/kayagoban/shadowlands))",
